<body>
    <!---->
    <section class="bg-half-170 bg-light d-table w-100">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row mt-5 justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                    <div class="pages-heading">
                        <h4 class="title mb-0"> Solar Blockchain Foundation </h4>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="position-breadcrumb">
                <nav aria-label="breadcrumb" class="d-inline-block">
                    <ul class="breadcrumb rounded shadow mb-0 px-4 py-2">
                        <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                        <li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="#">About</li>
                    </ul>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <div class="position-relative">
        <div class="shape overflow-hidden text-color-white">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 2880 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d="M0 48H1437.5H2880V0H2160C1442.5 52 720 0 720 0H0V48Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
            </svg>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!---->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-5 mt-4 pt-2 mt-sm-0 pt-sm-0">
                    <div class="position-relative">
                        <img src="assets/images/solar/foundation.png" class="rounded img-fluid mx-auto d-block" alt="">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-7 col-md-7 mt-4 pt-2 mt-sm-0 pt-sm-0">
                    <div class="section-title ms-lg-4">
                        <h4 class="title mb-4">The Foundation</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted">The Solar Blockchain Foundation is a non-profit organisation established in Estonia that focuses on creating a blockchain ecosystem with open-source developers and community involvement.<br>
                            <br> The Solar Blockchain offers a wide variety of features and tools that allows us to level with enterprise-grade applications.
                            <br>
                            <br> Discover our ecosystem by joining the community or by becoming part of the foundation.<br>
                            <br> Solar is for everyone.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section bg-light">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-end">
                <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-12 text-center">
                    <div class="section-title">
                        <h4 class="title title-dark mb-4">View Roadmap</h4>
                        <p class=" mb-0">The Swipe (SXP) card program was acquired by a 3rd party in 2022, paving the way for innovation. In response, the Solar Blockchain Foundation has initiated the launch of Solar SXP (mainnet), offering Swipe holders the voluntary
                            choice to migrate their assets. This marks a pivotal step in our journey, aligning with our mission to adapt to market and technological advancements, guided by community input and the foundational vision of Swipechain.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <a href="/roadmap" class="btn btn-primary">View Roadmap</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <div class="container mt-100 mt-60">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-7 order-2 order-md-1 mt-5 mt-sm-0">
                    <div class="section-title">
                        <h1 class="title mb-3">Join the Solar Blockchain Foundation</h1>
                        <p class="para-desc text-muted">
                            Our mission is not to control the Solar Blockchain or becoming the only organisation to fund critical Solar-related technologies.<br> Our mission is to guide the Solar Blockchain with the original vision from Swipechain. <br>                            Similar to the Ethereum Foundation, our ecosystem is designed to provide both financial and technical support to projects and entities within the greater Solar community, in order to accelerate the growth of the ecosystem.<br>
                            <br> Becoming an official member of the foundation allows you to collaborate with like-minded people and support the mission and vision of the Solar Blockchain Foundation.<br><br> Click on the button below to learn more and
                            apply for a position with the Solar Blockchain Foundation.</p>

                        <div class="mt-4">
                            <a href="javascript:void(0)" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#jointhefoundation" class="btn btn-primary">Learn more <i
                                    class="uil uil-angle-right-b"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-5 order-1 order-md-2">
                    <div class="app-feature-shape-right position-relative">
                        <div class="text-center text-md-end">
                            <img src="assets/images/solar/solarcore.png" class="img-fluid" alt="">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="modal fade" id="jointhefoundation" tabindex="-1" style="display: none;" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
            <div class="modal-content rounded shadow border-0">
                <div class="modal-body py-5">
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <div class="icon d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center bg-soft-danger rounded-circle mx-auto" style="height: 95px; width:95px;">
                            <h1 class="mb-0"><i class="uil uil-heart align-middle"></i></h1>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-4">
                            <h4>Join the Foundation</h4>
                            <p class="text-muted">
                                Anyone can contribute to our ecosystem without becoming a member of the foundation.<br> Due to the nature of the industry, it is important to comply with NDA's, regulatory requirements and restrictions.<br> Becoming part
                                of the foundation will allow you to get closer to the project and contribute to more critical components of the project with a much higher level of responsibility.<br> Are you looking to become part of the Solar Blockchain
                                Foundation and contribute to our mission and vision?<br> Read below to learn more.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                <b>The Solar Blockchain Foundation is actively looking for members that are able to
                                    contribute in the following areas.</b>
                            </p>
                            <ul style="text-align-last:initial;">
                                <li>Marketing, community and brand development</li>
                                <li>Legal challenges and advisory</li>
                                <li>Integration and partnership coordination</li>
                                <li>Research grants, projects, events and opportunities</li>
                                <li>Research technology and market demand</li>
                                <li>Public information certainty and accuracy</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p><b>Requirements to join our foundation in Estonia</b></p>
                            <ul style="text-align-last:initial;">
                                <li>Estonian e-residency <a href="https://www.e-resident.gov.ee/become-an-e-resident/" target="_blank" name="external" onclick="confirmExit(this.name)"><span
                                            class="badge rounded-pill bg-soft-primary">More info</span></a></li>
                                <li>Publicly disclose identity (real name)</li>
                                <li>Bound to strict internal NDA requirements</li>
                                <li>No criminal records</li>
                                <li>Not a Politically Exposed Person (PEP) <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Politically_exposed_persons" target="_blank" name="external" onclick="confirmExit(this.name)"><span
                                            class="badge rounded-pill bg-soft-primary">More info</span></a></li>
                                <li>Not sanctioned or from a country sanctioned by the EU</li>
                                <li>Able to contribute to the Solar Blockchain Foundation</li>
                            </ul>
                            <hr>
                            <p class="text-muted">
                                Ready to commit to the Solar Blockchain Foundation?<br> Click on the button below to apply!
                            </p>
                            <div class="mt-4">
                                <a href="https://forms.gle/Ywy1UpkVspwKtBfL9" target="_blank" name="external" onclick="confirmExit(this.name)" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Apply</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
